---
// Production landing page aligned with standard UK B2B courier layouts
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>SK1 Express | Nationwide Same Day Couriers</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Professional same day courier services based in Manchester. Dedicated vehicles, real-time tracking, and nationwide coverage.">
    
    <script is:inline src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <style>
        html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
        body { -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale; }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-slate-50 font-sans text-slate-800">

    <!-- Top Contact Bar -->
    <div class="bg-slate-900 text-slate-300 text-xs md:text-sm py-2 px-6 flex justify-between items-center">
        <div class="flex gap-4">
            <span>Email: dispatch@sk1express.uk</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4 font-bold text-white">
            <span>24/7 Operations</span>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Main Navigation -->
    <header class="w-full bg-white py-4 px-6 md:px-12 flex justify-between items-center border-b border-slate-200 sticky top-0 z-50 shadow-sm">
        <a href="/" class="text-3xl font-black tracking-tighter text-slate-900">SK1<span class="text-orange-600">EXPRESS</span></a>
        <nav class="hidden md:flex gap-8 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-600">
            <a href="#services" class="hover:text-orange-600 transition">Services</a>
            <a href="#fleet" class="hover:text-orange-600 transition">Our Fleet</a>
            <a href="#about" class="hover:text-orange-600 transition">About Us</a>
        </nav>
        <a href="tel:+440000000000" class="bg-orange-600 hover:bg-orange-700 text-white px-6 py-2.5 font-bold uppercase text-sm tracking-wide transition rounded-sm">Call Dispatch</a>
    </header>

    <main>
        <!-- Split Hero & Quote Form Section -->
        <section class="bg-slate-900 text-white py-12 md:py-20 px-6 relative border-b-8 border-orange-600">
            <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
                
                <!-- Hero Content -->
                <div>
                    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black mb-6 leading-tight">Dedicated Same Day Couriers in Manchester & Nationwide.</h1>
                    <p class="text-lg text-slate-300 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
                        When tomorrow is too late. We provide rapid-response dedicated vehicles for urgent, time-critical freight across the UK. Tracked from collection to delivery.
                    </p>
                    <ul class="space-y-3 font-bold text-slate-200 mb-8">
                        <li class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="text-orange-500">✓</span> Collection within 60 minutes nationwide</li>
                        <li class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="text-orange-500">✓</span> Goods in Transit Insured up to £50,000</li>
                        <li class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="text-orange-500">✓</span> Instant electronic Proof of Delivery (ePOD)</li>
                        <li class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="text-orange-500">✓</span> Direct A-to-B delivery (No co-loading)</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <!-- Instant Quote Form -->
                <div class="bg-white p-6 md:p-8 shadow-2xl rounded-sm text-slate-900">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-black mb-1 uppercase tracking-tight">Request a Quote</h2>
                    <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-6 font-medium">Enter your consignment details for an immediate response.</p>
                    
                    <form class="space-y-4" id="quoteForm">
                        <!-- Anti-Spam Honeypot -->
                        <div style="position: absolute; left: -5000px;" aria-hidden="true">
                            <input type="text" id="sk1_bot_trap" tabindex="-1" value="" autocomplete="off" />
                        </div>

                        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                            <div>
                                <label class="block text-xs font-bold text-slate-600 mb-1 uppercase">Collection Postcode</label>
                                <input type="text" id="collection" class="w-full bg-slate-50 border border-slate-300 p-3 font-bold focus:outline-none focus:border-orange-600 transition" placeholder="e.g. M1 1AA" required maxlength="8" />
                                <p id="col-error" class="text-red-600 text-xs mt-1 hidden font-bold">Invalid Postcode</p>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <label class="block text-xs font-bold text-slate-600 mb-1 uppercase">Delivery Postcode</label>
                                <input type="text" id="delivery" class="w-full bg-slate-50 border border-slate-300 p-3 font-bold focus:outline-none focus:border-orange-600 transition" placeholder="e.g. EC1A 1BB" required maxlength="8" />
                                <p id="del-error" class="text-red-600 text-xs mt-1 hidden font-bold">Invalid Postcode</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <label class="block text-xs font-bold text-slate-600 mb-1 uppercase">Consignment Details (Weight & Dimensions)</label>
                            <textarea id="cargo" class="w-full bg-slate-50 border border-slate-300 p-3 font-bold focus:outline-none focus:border-orange-600 transition h-20" placeholder="e.g. 1 standard pallet, 300kg" required></textarea>
                        </div>
                        <button type="submit" id="submitBtn" class="w-full bg-orange-600 hover:bg-orange-700 text-white font-black py-4 transition text-lg uppercase tracking-wide rounded-sm">Get Pricing</button>
                    </form>
                </div>

            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Core Services Grid -->
        <section id="services" class="max-w-7xl mx-auto py-20 px-6">
            <div class="text-center mb-12">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-slate-900 tracking-tight uppercase">Our Services</h2>
                <div class="w-16 h-1 bg-orange-600 mx-auto mt-4"></div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                <div class="bg-white p-8 border border-slate-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-slate-900 mb-3">Same Day Courier</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Urgent, dedicated transport for your time-critical goods. We collect within 60 minutes and drive directly to the delivery point with no diversions.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white p-8 border border-slate-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-slate-900 mb-3">Wait & Return</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Ideal for secure documents or components that require signing, processing, and returning immediately on the same dedicated vehicle.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white p-8 border border-slate-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-slate-900 mb-3">Scheduled Contracts</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Regular daily or weekly runs for businesses requiring dependable, recurring logistics support across the North West and beyond.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Fleet / Vehicle Specifications -->
        <section id="fleet" class="bg-slate-100 border-y border-slate-200 py-20 px-6">
            <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
                <div class="text-center mb-12">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-slate-900 tracking-tight uppercase">Vehicle Capabilities</h2>
                    <div class="w-16 h-1 bg-orange-600 mx-auto mt-4"></div>
                    <p class="mt-4 text-slate-600 font-medium">A diverse fleet to handle everything from legal documents to heavy industrial pallets.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
                    <!-- Small Van -->
                    <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 p-6">
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-slate-900 mb-1 border-b border-slate-100 pb-2">Small Van</h3>
                        <ul class="text-sm text-slate-600 space-y-2 mt-4 font-medium">
                            <li><strong class="text-slate-900">Max Payload:</strong> 400kg</li>
                            <li><strong class="text-slate-900">Pallet Capacity:</strong> 1 Standard</li>
                            <li><strong class="text-slate-900">Internal Length:</strong> 1.5m</li>
                            <li><strong class="text-slate-900">Ideal for:</strong> Parcels, boxes, urgent documents.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <!-- SWB -->
                    <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 p-6">
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-slate-900 mb-1 border-b border-slate-100 pb-2">Medium Van (SWB)</h3>
                        <ul class="text-sm text-slate-600 space-y-2 mt-4 font-medium">
                            <li><strong class="text-slate-900">Max Payload:</strong> 900kg</li>
                            <li><strong class="text-slate-900">Pallet Capacity:</strong> 2 Standard</li>
                            <li><strong class="text-slate-900">Internal Length:</strong> 2.4m</li>
                            <li><strong class="text-slate-900">Ideal for:</strong> Medium freight, multiple boxes.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <!-- LWB -->
                    <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 p-6">
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-slate-900 mb-1 border-b border-slate-100 pb-2">Large Van (LWB)</h3>
                        <ul class="text-sm text-slate-600 space-y-2 mt-4 font-medium">
                            <li><strong class="text-slate-900">Max Payload:</strong> 1,100kg</li>
                            <li><strong class="text-slate-900">Pallet Capacity:</strong> 3-4 Standard</li>
                            <li><strong class="text-slate-900">Internal Length:</strong> 3.3m</li>
                            <li><strong class="text-slate-900">Ideal for:</strong> Bulky goods, long lengths.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <!-- Luton -->
                    <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 p-6">
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-slate-900 mb-1 border-b border-slate-100 pb-2">Luton Tail-Lift</h3>
                        <ul class="text-sm text-slate-600 space-y-2 mt-4 font-medium">
                            <li><strong class="text-slate-900">Max Payload:</strong> 1,000kg</li>
                            <li><strong class="text-slate-900">Pallet Capacity:</strong> 6 Standard</li>
                            <li><strong class="text-slate-900">Internal Length:</strong> 4.0m</li>
                            <li><strong class="text-slate-900">Ideal for:</strong> Heavy machinery, palletized loads.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <script is:inline>
            // Form Validation and Submission Logic
            const formatPostcode = (val) => {
                let v = val.toUpperCase().replace(/[^A-Z0-9]/g, '');
                if (v.length > 4) v = v.slice(0, -3) + ' ' + v.slice(-3);
                return v;
            };

            const isValidPostcode = (p) => /^[A-Z]{1,2}[0-9][A-Z0-9]? ?[0-9][A-Z]{2}$/i.test(p);

            ['collection', 'delivery'].forEach(id => {
                document.getElementById(id).addEventListener('input', (e) => {
                    e.target.value = formatPostcode(e.target.value);
                    document.getElementById(`${id.substring(0,3)}-error`).classList.add('hidden');
                });
            });

            document.getElementById('quoteForm').addEventListener('submit', async (e) => {
                e.preventDefault();
                
                const col = document.getElementById('collection').value;
                const del = document.getElementById('delivery').value;
                let hasError = false;

                if (!isValidPostcode(col)) { document.getElementById('col-error').classList.remove('hidden'); hasError = true; }
                if (!isValidPostcode(del)) { document.getElementById('del-error').classList.remove('hidden'); hasError = true; }
                if (hasError) return;

                const btn = document.getElementById('submitBtn');
                btn.disabled = true;
                btn.innerText = 'Sending...';

                const payload = {
                    collection: col,
                    delivery: del,
                    cargo: document.getElementById('cargo').value,
                    trap: document.getElementById('sk1_bot_trap').value
                };

                try {
                    const response = await fetch('https://api.sk1express.uk', {
                        method: 'POST',
                        headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },
                        body: JSON.stringify(payload)
                    });

                    if (response.ok) {
                        alert('Quote request received successfully. Our team will contact you shortly.');
                        document.getElementById('quoteForm').reset();
                    } else {
                        alert('Server error. Please call us directly for a quote.');
                    }
                } catch (err) {
                    alert('Network error. Please call us directly for a quote.');
                } finally {
                    btn.disabled = false;
                    btn.innerText = 'Get Pricing';
                }
            });
        </script>
    </main>

    <!-- Standard Corporate Footer -->
    <footer class="bg-slate-900 text-slate-400 py-12 px-6 border-t-4 border-orange-600">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-8 border-b border-slate-800 pb-8">
            <div>
                <h4 class="text-white font-black text-xl mb-4">SK1 EXPRESS</h4>
                <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed">Your trusted partner for dedicated same day courier services. Operating from Manchester to anywhere in the UK.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h4 class="text-white font-bold mb-4 uppercase tracking-wider text-sm">Contact Details</h4>
                <ul class="text-sm space-y-2">
                    <li>Call: 0161 000 0000</li>
                    <li>Email: dispatch@sk1express.uk</li>
                    <li>Available 24 hours a day, 7 days a week.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h4 class="text-white font-bold mb-4 uppercase tracking-wider text-sm">Quick Links</h4>
                <ul class="text-sm space-y-2">
                    <li><a href="#services" class="hover:text-orange-500 transition">Our Services</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#fleet" class="hover:text-orange-500 transition">Vehicle Guide</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#" class="hover:text-orange-500 transition">Terms & Conditions</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto text-xs text-center">
            <p>&copy; 2026 SK1 Express. All rights reserved. Registered in England & Wales.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
